commit_message:
Fix RSpec 3.x syntax

* 1 conversion
    from: it { should ... }
      to: it { is_expected.to ... }

* 1 conversion
    from: its(:attr) { }
      to: describe '#attr' do subject { super().attr }; it { } end

Change-Id: I92fdb3dd3f24cbfb736ddb1b4fbb87ea1cc9f09f
Signed-off-by: Gael Chamoulaud <gchamoul@redhat.com>

